{"type":"message","id":"1614531c","parentId":"98fcc07c","timestamp":"2026-06-04T23:42:47.758Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"关键发现：\n1. **tts 6月4日 09:01 那个 session 用的就是 MiniMax-M2.7**（modelId 字段）\n2. **tts 的 config.json 文件最近是 5月2日 17:08，models.json 是 5月8日** —— 都不算最近\n3. tts 用的是 mcporter + sorftime-mcp 的 MCP 配置（5月20日 key）\n\n那么\"昨天才刚换上的\"是指什么？让我看下 tts 5月29日、6月3日的 session，可能有模型切换。\n\n等等，5月29日的 session 有 `.reset` 后缀，可能就是关键。我去找 tts 的所有 session 中\"model_change\"的事件。","thinkingSignature":"a5f05580b3c70b44e60320e49280fdab329dcd900d46250c9d84664131f37e8c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1rre6tsnptf8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"---tts agent 配置文件---\"\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/config.json 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"---models.json---\"\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/models.json 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"---auth-profiles.json---\"\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/auth-profiles.json 2>/dev/null\necho \"\"\necho \"---tts sessions 按 mtime 倒序前15---\"\ncd /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/\nls -lt --time=mtime *.jsonl 2>/dev/null | head -15 | awk '{print $6,$7,$8,$9}'"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1rre6tsnptf8_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"---扫描 tts 所有 session 的 model_change 事件，找最近的模型切换---\"\ncd /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/\npython3 << 'EOF'\nimport json, os, glob, datetime\nfiles = glob.glob('*.jsonl')\n# 排除 .reset/.deleted/.bak\nfiles = [f for f in files if '.reset.' not in f and '.deleted.' not in f and '.bak-' not in f]\nprint(f'扫描 {len(files)} 个 .jsonl 文件')\nevents = []\nfor fn in files:\n    try:\n        with open(fn) as f:\n            for line in f:\n                try:\n                    o = json.loads(line)\n                    if o.get('type') == 'model_change':\n                        mtime = os.path.getmtime(fn)\n                        events.append({\n                            'file': fn[:8]+'...',\n                            'mtime': datetime.datetime.fromtimestamp(mtime).strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M'),\n                            'session_ts': o.get('timestamp'),\n                            'provider': o.get('provider'),\n                            'modelId': o.get('modelId'),\n                        })\n                except: pass\n    except: pass\nevents.sort(key=lambda x: x['mtime'], reverse=True)\nprint(f'共 {len(events)} 个 model_change 事件')\nfor e in events[:15]:\n    print(f\"  {e['mtime']} | {e['file']} | {e['session_ts']} | {e['provider']}/{e['modelId']}\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1113,"output":697,"cacheRead":69656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780616548171,"responseId":"0671406485c26920bc1fe6216db0c3e3"}}
