{"type":"message","id":"e37a5692","parentId":"163ad18e","timestamp":"2026-06-05T00:32:17.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying:\n- \"昨天晚上还上的3.0，之前用的是2.7\"\n- Last night they switched to 3.0 (MiniMax-M3), before that they were using 2.7 (MiniMax-M2.7)\n\nSo the user switched tts from M2.7 to M3 last night. But my data shows the latest model_change events are still M2.7.\n\nPossible explanations:\n1. The change was made to the tts config but hasn't taken effect yet (e.g., the agent needs a restart)\n2. The model was changed but in a way that doesn't create a model_change event (e.g., via sessions_send or some other mechanism that doesn't trigger the event)\n\n\n3. The new session that should show M3 hasn't run yet or the model_change event isn't being captured properly\n\nLooking at the timeline, I can see the agent was running M2.7 in the earlier sessions, and there was a cron job trigger at 22:54, but I need to verify whether the actual model change to M3 has actually propagated through the system yet.\n\nThe model_change event showing M2.7 could mean the config change wasn't applied to an already-running agent, the new session with M3 simply hasn't generated a model_change event in the transcript, or the session where the change was made hasn't been recorded yet.\n\nI should check the cron job's actual execution model directly rather than relying on the transcript, and also verify whether M3 is properly configured in tts's models.json so I can understand the current state of what's actually running versus what was configured.\n","thinkingSignature":"17363923cbc04332f4393d680bbe7173845b40ca22b8e52f860ebbed439e797b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了，昨晚从 2.7 换到了 M3（MiniMax-M3）。让我确认配置现状，以及新模型是否已经生效。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xh91v3b63s0k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/config.json\necho \"===\"\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/models.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xh91v3b63s0k_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 6月5日的 session（如果有的话，说明新模型已启动）===\"\ncd /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/\nls -lt --time=mtime 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"Jun|6月|05\" | head -10\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 找最新 session（今日或昨夜）===\"\nls -lt --time=mtime *.jsonl 2>/dev/null | head -3\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 找今日 model_change 事件 ===\"\npython3 << 'EOF'\nimport json, glob, datetime, os\nfiles = glob.glob('*.jsonl')\nevents = []\nfor fn in files:\n    try:\n        with open(fn) as f:\n            for line in f:\n                try:\n                    o = json.loads(line)\n                    if o.get('type') == 'model_change':\n                        mtime = os.path.getmtime(fn)\n                        events.append({\n                            'file': fn,\n                            'mtime': datetime.datetime.fromtimestamp(mtime).strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M'),\n                            'ts': o.get('timestamp','')[:19],\n                            'provider': o.get('provider'),\n                            'modelId': o.get('modelId'),\n                        })\n                except: pass\n    except: pass\nevents.sort(key=lambda x: x['mtime'], reverse=True)\n# 过滤6月4日之后\nfor e in events[:5]:\n    print(f\"{e['mtime']} | {e['file'][:8]}... | {e['ts']} | {e['provider']}/{e['modelId']}\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":77269,"output":786,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78055,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780619517193,"responseId":"06714bfdfcc89bdb94e8efc2cf427ad7"}}
