{"type":"message","id":"3e1b0e20","parentId":"9832550b","timestamp":"2026-06-05T00:32:36.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the situation clearly:\n\n1. User says: last night (昨晚) they switched tts from 2.7 to 3.0\n2. The tts agent's `models.json` currently only shows M2.7 - there's NO MiniMax-M3 model configured\n3. The tts agent's `config.json` still says `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash` (which is stale/outdated)\n4. The latest session (June 4 23:10) still shows M2.7\n\nSo the issue is clear: **the user updated the global configuration or some central setting for MiniMax-M3, but the tts agent's `models.json` was never updated to include M3, and/or the tts agent process wasn't restarted to pick up the new model**.\n\n\nThe `models.json` needs to have the M3 model added as a valid option, and the tts agent likely needs a restart to recognize it. But I'm realizing the config shows `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash` while all the cron sessions are running M2.7 - so there's a discrepancy between what's configured and what's actually being used that I need to understand better. The config still references the outdated gemini model, but since all cron sessions are actually running M2.7, it seems the config.json might not be controlling the model at all. The real issue is that `models.json` only has M2.7 available, so even though the user wants M3, there's no way to select it—I need to add M3 to the available models in that file.\n","thinkingSignature":"dfd85e8dadae19f6248af236a042197f35a609c1d6cd24c00964970ad8b7b39a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明确了：\n\n- **models.json 里只有 M2.7，M3 根本没加进去**\n- config.json 里写的是 gemini-2.0-flash（过时配置）\n- 所有 session 跑的都是 M2.7，说明实际生效的是 models.json，而它里面没有 3.0\n\n问题就在这里：你想让 tts 用 3.0，但 tts 的 `models.json` 根本没配 3.0，所以它只能继续用 2.7。\n\n现在加进去：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z61ntz7e4aeh_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/models.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z61ntz7e4aeh_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== main agent 的 models.json（参考 M3 怎么写的）===\"\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/models.json 2>/dev/null | head -60\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 看 main 的 config 里的 model 字段 ===\"\ncat /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/main/agent/config.json 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5306,"output":583,"cacheRead":73256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79145,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780619539065,"responseId":"06714c1393c071bff773337df3a56564"}}
