{"type":"message","id":"e1fbdb76","parentId":"53526ece","timestamp":"2026-06-05T00:33:43.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway restart is done. Now let me summarize what happened to the user. The configuration is fixed:1. models.json: Replaced the old minimax/minimax-cn providers with minimax(49套餐) containing both M3 and M2.7\n2. config.json: Updated model from \"gemini/gemini-2.0-flash\" to \"minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3\", and workspaceDir from \"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector\" to \"/home/halei/workspace-tts\"\n3. Triggered gateway restart to apply changes\n\nWait - the user said \"昨天网上还上的 3.0\" which means \"last night online they put on 3.0\". This could mean:\n\n\nA) User already made changes to models.json and tts should have M3, but it didn't\nB) User is confusing with someone else\nC) User wants me to do it NOW\n\nBut looking at the actual files - the models.json still had M2.7 only, and config still had gemini. So the user's \"last night online they put on 3.0\" might be referring to some other action or intention that didn't actually get saved. Regardless - I've now fixed the config. The restart will apply the new settings. Let me give the user a clear update.\n","thinkingSignature":"0bbbc6304591b4b142d22a9b107c2d7d7334d41532849806886cd82fa2c0f101"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n配置已修正，gateway 已重启。实际状态：\n\n**问题根因：**\n- `models.json` 里 tts 的 provider 还是旧的两套（minimax / minimax-cn），里面只有 M2.7，根本没有 M3\n- `config.json` 里 model 写的是 `gemini/gemini-2.0-flash`（从没生效过，一直 fallback 到 M2.7）\n- workspaceDir 指向 `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector`（不存在）\n\n**刚才做的事：**\n1. `models.json` — 换成 `minimax(49套餐)` provider，包含 **M3（主）+ M2.7（备用）**，apiKey 保留原值\n2. `config.json` — `model` 改为 `minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3`，workspaceDir 纠正为 `/home/halei/workspace-tts`\n3. 发了 `SIGUSR1` 软重启，让 tts 加载新配置\n\n下一条 cron（9AM 或手动触发）会验证是否真的切到 M3。需要现在手动触发一次 tts 看是否正常出结果吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7",