{"type":"message","id":"c7546da4","parentId":"ee5efa26","timestamp":"2026-06-05T00:36:03.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户提到了 M3 按 token 计费的问题。从 cron job 状态看：\n- tts 的 cron 每天 9/12/15/18/21 点跑 5 次\n- 6月4日那次 lastDurationMs: 1006789ms ≈ 16.8 分钟\n- lastRunStatus: ok\n- lastDeliveryStatus: delivered\n\n但 session.jsonl 里的 usage 字段都是 0（可能本地 jsonl 不记录 token 消耗，由 provider 计费）。\n\n用户的担忧点很合理：M3 按 token 计费，tts 每 3 小时一次、每次要扫描 30 个商品 + 调多个 API + 处理趋势数据，单次可能 100K+ tokens，每天 5 次 = 500K tokens/day。\n\n需要考虑：\n1. M2.7 → M3 的实际成本差异\n2. tts 的 cron 频率是否需要调整\n3. 是否需要给 tts 设 token 预算/限制\n\n让我给用户一个清晰的成本分析 + 几个选项。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ce99aexfvmts_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== tts 6月4日 session 实际内容（估算实际数据量）===\"\npython3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\nfn='/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/236e682a-4f16-460b-88bd-3595ca024543.jsonl'\n# 估算每个 tool_result 的字符数（粗略 1token≈4字符）\ntool_results = []\nwith open(fn) as f:\n    for line in f:\n        try:\n            o = json.loads(line)\n            if o.get('type') == 'message':\n                msg = o.get('message',{})\n                content = msg.get('content','')\n                if isinstance(content, str):\n                    if 'toolResult' in o.get('type','') or 'tool' in str(msg).lower():\n                        tool_results.append(len(content))\n        except: pass\nprint(f'收集到 {len(tool_results)} 个 tool_result 样本')\nif tool_results:\n    total_chars = sum(tool_results)\n    print(f'总字符数: {total_chars} ≈ {total_chars/4:.0f} tokens (粗估)')\n    print(f'最大单次: {max(tool_results)} 字符 ≈ {max(tool_results)/4:.0f} tokens')\nEOF\necho \"\"\necho \"=== tts cron job 频率 ===\"\necho \"每天 5 次（9/12/15/18/21 点）\"\necho \"每次平均时长 16.8 分钟（6月4日实测）\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":658,"output":565,"cacheRead":88094,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89317,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780619746292,"responseId":"06714ce3d11a616326b664565da9a723"}}
