{"type":"message","id":"13d4f130","parentId":"4969bc30","timestamp":"2026-06-05T01:12:50.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"等你选。顺便：不管你选哪条，复核任务我都写好了，下面是现成的**任务描述**（复制就能用）：\n\n---\n\n> 你是 Agent 编排工程师，负责所有 Agent 的设置调整。2026-06-05 早些时候 main（首席调度官）作为应急响应直接改了 tts 的两个文件，事后根据新角色分工应该由你接手。请做一次复核并把结果告诉 HALEI：\n> \n> **复核项：**\n> 1. `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/config.json` — model 应该是 `minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3`，workspaceDir 应该是 `/home/halei/workspace-tts`\n> 2. `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/agent/models.json` — `minimax(49套餐)` provider 应包含 M3 + M2.7，apiKey 仍有效\n> 3. tts 的 cron job `5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6` — sessionTarget 仍指 tts，没被破坏\n> 4. tts 最近一次 session `236e682a-4f16-460b-88bd-3595ca024543` — 看下 status，新配置是否生效\n> \n> **输出：** 复核结论 + 需要补漏的项，发到 tts 那个 Bot 报告给 HALEI。\n> \n> **顺带：** 给 agent-orchestrator 自己写一份自定义 SOUL（替换掉 `/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator/SOUL.md` 的默认模板），体现\"Agent 编排工程师\"角色。可以一并做掉。\n> \n> **工作目录：** `/home/halei/workspace-agent-orchestrator`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":110,"output":386,"cacheRead":118536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119032,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780621960651,"responseId":"06715589f352471e454fc5fa5b336e6c"}}
